fields.name: iTOW
fields.description: GPS time of week of the navigation epoch from which the sync manager obtains the GNSS specific data.

fields.name: intDeltaFreq
fields.description: Frequency increment of the internal oscillator

fields.description: Uncertainty of the internal oscillator frequency increment

fields.name: intRaw

fields.name: extDeltaFreq

fields.name: extDeltaFreqUnc

fields.name: extRaw

adjudication.reasoning: The provided extraction accurately represents the UBX-TIM-FCHG message as defined in the u-blox 8 M8 Receiver Description and Protocol Specification. The class ID (0x0D), message ID (0x16), and payload length (32 bytes) are correct. The field definitions, including the fixed scaling factor (2^-8) for frequency increments and uncertainties, match the standard documentation.
